  <brief_title>A Prospective Single Arm Study of Intraoperative Radiotherapy for Locally Advanced or Recurrent Rectal Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Prospective Single Arm Study of Intraoperative Radiotherapy for Locally Advanced or Recurrent Rectal Cancer</official_title>
